data.description: WELCOME TO PARADISE! Canal home with boat lift close to the open bay!  5 minute drive to the Seawall and Beach! Screened-in porch and large open air deck with gorgeous water views. Unobstructed view of the Sweetwater Nature Preserve and breathtaking sunsets and Bay views from almost every room in the house.  New roof, hardi board siding, interior paint and updated bathrooms in 2019 with many more upgrades!  Interior elevator to all floors. Come see this beautiful home today! MOTIVATED SELLER!!
